metadata.name: flower
metadata.description:
This is 1 NFT in a collection of 12  that has been issued as a single unique edition.

Size 5600x8400 px

You did not come into this life to learn anything - you have nothing to learn; you have come to manifest what you already know. By manifesting this, you will put your abilities into action and create yourself anew through your experience. This is how you give meaning to your life. So you will open yourself like a flower and free yourself from the shackles
